1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,740
=Episode 21=

16
00:01:59,359 --> 00:02:00,159
Zhang.

17
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,040
If for some reason...

18
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:04,000
(Lysen Group)

19
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,799
I don't make it out

20
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:05,840
of this building today,

21
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:09,879
there are two letters
in the safe inside the car.

22
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,599
One is for my wife,

23
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:14,479
the other is for my lawyer.

24
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:16,000
The passcode

25
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,439
is Chloe's birthday.

26
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,360
(You know it.)

27
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,120
(Yes, sir.)

28
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:19,970
(I'm counting on you.)

29
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,080
(Mr. Jiang, you...)

30
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:35,560
Mr. Jiang,

31
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,240
Mr. Li's funds have cleared.

32
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:41,840
Go.

33
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:42,840
- On it.
- Yes, sir.

34
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:50,700
(Lysen 13%, Yinyu 19%)

35
00:02:54,660 --> 00:02:59,020
(Lysen 17%-19%, Yinyu 19%)

36
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,199
Thank you.

37
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:06,740
(Lysen Group Project Funding Approval)
Rejected by Jiang Dongchao)

38
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:12,340
(Lysen Group Project Funding Approval)
Rejected by Jiang Dongchao)

39
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,960
Why were these rejected?

40
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:18,280
That was Mr. Jiang's decision.

41
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,199
Is he in his office?

42
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,120
No.

43
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,159
He's in the trading room.

44
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,639
(As of today's market close,)

45
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:34,280
(Lysen Group's stake in Bosi
has reached twenty-three percent.)

46
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:37,120
(This move effectively silences
the rumors suggesting)

47
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,000
(that Jiang Dongchao)

48
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,879
(lacked sufficient capital
for the takeover.)

49
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,960
(Lysen has now
surpassed Yinyu Technology)

50
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,919
(by a four percent margin,)

51
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,800
(becoming the majority
shareholder of Bosi.)

52
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,520
Boss,

53
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,039
didn't we run the numbers?

54
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,639
He wasn't supposed
to reach nineteen percent.

55
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:50,319
How did he get twenty-three percent?

56
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:51,960
Li Wancheng loathes him.

57
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,560
Why on earth would he fund him?

58
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:56,840
When a crisis hits,
enemies become allies.

59
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,199
It's not that far-fetched.

60
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,919
What are you panicking for?

61
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,159
Here, help me finish this puzzle.

62
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,800
Don't worry.

63
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:06,960
Trust me.

64
00:04:08,879 --> 00:04:09,759
I have a trump card.

65
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,600
Mr. Jiang, give me one good reason.

66
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,800
It was a decision
from upper management.

67
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,600
So, you were just

68
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,720
using me all along.

69
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,240
You used me
to get the money from Mr. Li,

70
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,839
only to divert it to the Bosi takeover.

71
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,560
Isn't that right?

72
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,680
Everything you said

73
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,879
about supporting me

74
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,800
was just a lie.

75
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,240
The Bosi takeover is
the priority for Lysen.

76
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,879
The true value of this deal

77
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:47,600
is beyond your imagination.

78
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:50,879
The most sustainable way to acquire Bosi
is to cooperate with Yang Jinwan,

79
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,759
to help Bosi transform,

80
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,000
not to turn this into

81
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,360
some meaningless numbers game.

82
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:57,879
Look.

83
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,160
The numbers are the game.

84
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,560
(Lysen 23%  Yinyu 19%)

85
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,360
Yuci,

86
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,959
everyone calls you a math genius.

87
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,000
I thought you of all people
understood numbers.

88
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:07,920
If you don't finish this game,

89
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,839
what right do you have

90
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,079
to pursue your dreams?

91
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,519
Don't worry.

92
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:13,279
Once the takeover is successful,

93
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,240
I'll make sure they happen.

94
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:18,839
Mr. Jiang,

95
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,199
can I even trust you anymore?

96
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,120
After all, there's nothing

97
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,800
but numbers in your eyes.

98
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:40,040
Do you have any idea

99
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,959
how much tax

100
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,160
Lysen Group has to pay every year

101
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,079
under my leadership?

102
00:05:44,279 --> 00:05:45,680
Or my charity projects?

103
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:48,120
Do you know how many useless good people

104
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:49,600
he supports annually?

105
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,000
Do you even know?

106
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,519
What is a good person?

107
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:57,279
To the children in rural mountains, I am

108
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,720
the ultimate good person.

109
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,560
Because they received

110
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,439
my gifts.

111
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,079
I brought them food,

112
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,920
textbooks, and toys.

113
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,560
And your so-called good people?

114
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,759
Aside from empty ideals,

115
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:08,500
what have they contributed
to this society?

116
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,000
Am I not kind enough,

117
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,150
or is your so-called kindness
nothing more than

118
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,959
hypocritical, empty talk?

119
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:23,079
Fine.

120
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,360
Mr. Jiang,

121
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,800
you might pay a lot in taxes,

122
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:27,759
but let's be honest.

123
00:06:27,850 --> 00:06:30,000
You also command
this society's most elite resources.

124
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,759
Don't you?

125
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:32,360
The system

126
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,000
practically forces your hand.

127
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:37,000
Those charity projects?

128
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:39,040
They're just small change used

129
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,839
to facilitate your tax write-offs

130
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,079
somewhere else.

131
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,990
At the end of the day,

132
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,560
your kindness is just a calculated

133
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:47,920
transactional loop.

134
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,079
Does that even count as being good?

135
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:52,879
To me, kindness isn't a strategy.

136
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,639
You keep saying I'm chasing a fantasy,

137
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,079
but I'm going to prove to you

138
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,040
that I'm not just talk.

139
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,079
Fine.

140
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,680
I get it.

141
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,800
I get it now too.

142
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,000
Mr. Jiang.

143
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,399
Mr. Pengyu.

144
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,720
Ms. Xin wants you back at the office.

145
00:07:34,839 --> 00:07:36,800
She and Sir Yang are waiting for you.

146
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,399
Let's go.

147
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,920
After you.

148
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,560
Stand up.

149
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,759
Stand up!

150
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,199
Apologize to Sir Yang.

151
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,720
Seriously?

152
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,560
I thought

153
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,720
calling someone's parents

154
00:08:26,650 --> 00:08:28,360
is what you do
with elementary school kids.

155
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,199
Mr. Yang, you're pretty old-school.

156
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:33,200
You used my mother to pressure me.

157
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,840
Listen, son.

158
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,519
I've known your mother

159
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,919
since she was a little girl.

160
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,720
I was an early investor

161
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,960
in your grandfather's factory.

162
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:48,919
I was even there

163
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:50,159
when your parents first met.

164
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,399
I get it.

165
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:54,320
Youngsters can be impulsive.

166
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,559
But whatever your vendetta
against Jiang Dongchao is,

167
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:59,600
you shouldn't have targeted Bosi.

168
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,600
Mr. Yang,

169
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,200
maybe

170
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,080
Bosi's business model

171
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,279
is just plain obsolete.

172
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,759
An acquisition was inevitable.

173
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,639
Even without me,

174
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:11,360
you stood no chance
against Jiang Dongchao.

175
00:09:11,799 --> 00:09:13,320
At your age,

176
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,799
why not just retire?

177
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:17,120
Let the new generation lead.

178
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,880
- Wouldn't that be better?
- Watch your mouth!

179
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,399
Ms. Xin,

180
00:09:24,759 --> 00:09:27,080
everything I've done is
legal and above board.

181
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,799
So why should I stay quiet?

182
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,279
In corporate warfare,

183
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:31,919
it's either win or lose.

184
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,919
No room for sentiment.

185
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:39,159
Win or lose.

186
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,320
Sentiment.

187
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,360
I was willing to dilute
my own majority stake

188
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,360
just to ensure

189
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,639
that Bosi could keep growing.

190
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,240
I never expected

191
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,279
vultures like you

192
00:09:56,279 --> 00:09:57,759
to swoop in when we were vulnerable.

193
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,840
Lysen Group now holds

194
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:02,600
twenty-three percent.

195
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:06,240
You and your little crew

196
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,440
barely have nineteen percent

197
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,879
between the lot of you.

198
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,519
And you really think you can win?

199
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:14,679
You see,

200
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,200
I have a mother

201
00:10:16,799 --> 00:10:18,159
who taught me from a young age

202
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:19,279
that I should always

203
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:20,720
have a trump card.

204
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:25,240
Don't you forget about

205
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:27,000
Bai Qingyu's ten percent stake.

206
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,559
(Strategic Press Conference)
Greetings, everyone.

207
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:33,919
(Baiye Group)
I am the representative for Madam Bai,

208
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:35,399
Bai Liangliang.

209
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:37,759
Baiye Group has
always prioritized stability.

210
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,440
Our company's internal compass

211
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,240
has always pointed toward balance.

212
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,960
Therefore, Baiye

213
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,240
does not easily involve itself

214
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:48,480
in any unsuitable business transactions

215
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,600
or conflicts.

216
00:10:50,279 --> 00:10:51,480
However,

217
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,399
the scales have tipped out of control.

218
00:10:54,879 --> 00:10:56,360
To ensure market stability

219
00:10:56,559 --> 00:10:58,000
and protect shareholder interests.

220
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,399
Baiye is making its stance clear.

221
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:02,440
Baiye Group will stand firmly

222
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,120
side-by-side with Bosi Real Estate

223
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:05,399
to repel all external threats.

224
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,840
A moment ago, you said

225
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:22,399
that power only recognizes
winners and losers.

226
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,399
Pengyu.

227
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,840
You were wrong.

228
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,600
Aside from winners and losers,

229
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:31,200
there is a world of social intricacies

230
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,480
beyond your comprehension.

231
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,039
What you see

232
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:38,480
is your solid foundation.

233
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:40,279
But what I see

234
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,679
is a predator waiting

235
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:42,799
in the hunting grounds.

236
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,200
Throughout your tug-of-war
with Lysen Group,

237
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:48,279
Bosi's market value has skyrocketed.

238
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:51,000
That foundation of yours

239
00:11:51,679 --> 00:11:54,279
was simply watching from the sidelines.

240
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,080
Pengyu.

241
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:00,480
You lost.

242
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:14,559
Here's the thing.

243
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:18,879
Mr. Yang,

244
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,960
do you want to know why

245
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,960
I never call you "sir"?

246
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:25,080
Because in my eyes,

247
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,279
you're just a low-class upstart.

248
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:29,000
Stop pretending to be a gentleman.

249
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:30,519
You were right about one thing.

250
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:31,879
This is a hunting ground,

251
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,720
and the winner hasn't been decided yet.

252
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:34,600
But one thing

253
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,840
is crystal clear to me.

254
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,679
I'll be the one

255
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:39,519
to settle

256
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:41,200
my father's debt.

257
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,159
For you two,

258
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,320
the era of the old guard

259
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,080
is over.

260
00:12:57,279 --> 00:12:58,240
Savage.

261
00:12:59,080 --> 00:12:59,919
How uncouth.

262
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:03,759
Xian Pengyu!

263
00:13:05,159 --> 00:13:05,960
Bosi...

264
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,399
Bosi Real Estate will never

265
00:13:08,399 --> 00:13:09,799
fall into your hands!

266
00:13:09,879 --> 00:13:11,200
You're delusional!

267
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:15,080
Look something up for me.

268
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,639
Get me a list of shareholders holding

269
00:13:17,639 --> 00:13:19,240
at least one percent of Bosi.

270
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:21,519
I need more equity.

271
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:23,700
It's the only way
I'll have any leverage at the table.

272
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,399
What is this?

273
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,559
Are you refusing to help?

274
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:48,260
(Cryptex Fund 4%)

275
00:13:48,919 --> 00:13:50,240
I know what you're planning.

276
00:13:50,799 --> 00:13:51,720
Save your breath.

277
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:08,840
This is the Master's

278
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,039
a Da Vinci cryptex.

279
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,440
To open it,

280
00:14:11,519 --> 00:14:13,320
you have to crack a five-digit code.

281
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:15,000
It has five rotating dials,

282
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,720
each with twenty-six letters.

283
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:19,120
That means there are

284
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,759
11,881,736

