574
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:45,240
I'm done with these

575
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:50,079
useless emotions.

576
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:20,160
I only came here to warn you.

577
00:28:21,519 --> 00:28:22,559
Back out now.

578
00:28:23,599 --> 00:28:24,680
Hand over your shares

579
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,799
to Madam Bai.

580
00:28:26,799 --> 00:28:28,039
It's not too late to fix this.

581
00:28:31,759 --> 00:28:32,799
And if I refuse?

582
00:28:34,359 --> 00:28:35,440
You had a thousand chances

583
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:36,880
to walk away unscathed,

584
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,359
yet you chose to stay

585
00:28:38,359 --> 00:28:40,319
just for the opportunity to betray me.

586
00:28:41,759 --> 00:28:42,680
So, it's time

587
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:45,200
I threw a few wild cards into the mix.

588
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:46,759
Don't you agree,

589
00:28:47,599 --> 00:28:48,400
Ms. Bai?

590
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,079
Don't you ever

591
00:28:53,039 --> 00:28:53,839
come back here

592
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,960
again.

593
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:00,720
Get out.

594
00:29:01,980 --> 00:29:06,780
♪I'm coming back enraged♪

595
00:29:06,780 --> 00:29:12,660
♪Bring the fire
to the game and paint it red♪

596
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:14,900
♪With blood♪

597
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:18,740
♪From the start to the end,
you're damned♪

598
00:29:18,740 --> 00:29:22,660
♪I'm coming back untamed♪

599
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:29,400
♪And I'm standing
on the traumatized ruins, unbent♪

600
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,200
Miss Rao.

601
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:33,760
I assume there's been a problem
with the startup capital?

602
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,240
I'm sorry, Mr. Li.

603
00:29:37,759 --> 00:29:39,039
The startup funds

604
00:29:39,599 --> 00:29:40,960
were diverted by Mr. Jiang

605
00:29:41,119 --> 00:29:42,559
to finance the Bosi takeover.

606
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,119
I was too eager to get started,

607
00:29:45,799 --> 00:29:46,900
and he used that against me.

608
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,720
I expected as much.

609
00:29:51,260 --> 00:29:54,220
(Three Days Ago)

610
00:30:06,119 --> 00:30:06,920
Sir, we're just

611
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:08,319
giving this money to Miss Rao?

612
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,559
But what about Mr. Jiang?

613
00:30:09,799 --> 00:30:10,680
Jiang Dongchao

614
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:12,960
will definitely misappropriate
these funds

615
00:30:13,759 --> 00:30:14,960
to fuel the Bosi takeover.

616
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:17,039
He has no intention
of giving them to Rao Yuci.

617
00:30:18,119 --> 00:30:19,440
His acquisition fund

618
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:20,640
is completely drained.

619
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,119
He's desperate for this cash.

620
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,920
If you already knew that,

621
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:27,200
why would you give it to her?

622
00:30:28,519 --> 00:30:30,680
This money won't
just vanish into thin air.

623
00:30:31,039 --> 00:30:32,160
As Bosi's stock price

624
00:30:33,079 --> 00:30:34,039
continues to climb,

625
00:30:34,279 --> 00:30:36,640
the value of the shares Lysen purchased

626
00:30:37,039 --> 00:30:38,160
will only keep rising.

627
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,680
So, by letting Jiang Dongchao

628
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,599
misuse this capital,

629
00:30:43,200 --> 00:30:46,319
not only does Lysen Group profit,

630
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:49,119
but Rao Yuci will finally see
Jiang Dongchao

631
00:30:49,119 --> 00:30:50,400
for exactly who he really is.

632
00:30:52,039 --> 00:30:53,039
It's a win-win situation.

633
00:30:54,079 --> 00:30:54,880
Besides,

634
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:58,559
since we believe
in Miss Rao's potential,

635
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:00,480
isn't this

636
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:01,559
the perfect opportunity

637
00:31:01,559 --> 00:31:02,480
to win her over?

638
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,039
Miss Rao.

639
00:31:15,079 --> 00:31:16,720
I'll be blunt with you.

640
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,279
Jiang Dongchao is a man
of dangerous ambition.

641
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,359
I don't always agree

642
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:23,519
with his

643
00:31:23,839 --> 00:31:25,160
vision for the company.

644
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,559
But for the sake

645
00:31:26,559 --> 00:31:29,000
of the big picture,
and for the future of Lysen Group,

646
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:32,480
sometimes I have no choice
but to endure it.

647
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:38,400
I truly understand

648
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,640
how you must feel, Mr. Li.

649
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,000
But my only focus

650
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,720
is seeing

651
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,839
my responsibilities through.

652
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,519
So, given the current mess,

653
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,519
what's your next move?

654
00:31:53,039 --> 00:31:54,480
Since you've been honest with me,

655
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,640
I'll be honest with you.

656
00:31:57,359 --> 00:31:59,720
I've secured a four percent stake
in Bosi Real Estate.

657
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,640
I plan

658
00:32:01,839 --> 00:32:03,279
to hand it over to Xian Pengyu.

659
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:06,000
A classic flanking maneuver.

660
00:32:07,119 --> 00:32:08,200
If you use that

661
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,079
to trade for the snack street,

662
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:12,279
Xian Pengyu won't be able to say no.

663
00:32:13,559 --> 00:32:14,359
Exactly.

664
00:32:16,359 --> 00:32:17,839
But this also means

665
00:32:17,839 --> 00:32:19,279
that in this takeover battle,

666
00:32:19,559 --> 00:32:21,279
Lysen Group might lose
to Yinyu Technology.

667
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,079
That's why

668
00:32:23,079 --> 00:32:24,200
I've come

669
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:25,079
to speak with you.

670
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:27,880
I didn't want to leave you in the dark.

671
00:32:33,279 --> 00:32:34,880
Go ahead. Follow your instincts.

672
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,240
I'll provide

673
00:32:37,559 --> 00:32:38,799
additional funding.

674
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,480
Consider it a dedicated grant.

675
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:42,720
Get those stalled projects

676
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,359
back on their feet.

677
00:32:47,759 --> 00:32:49,039
(Baiye Group announced yesterday)

678
00:32:49,039 --> 00:32:50,000
(their support for Bosi.)

679
00:32:50,359 --> 00:32:53,400
(The conflict has instantly shifted
from a duel into a three-way brawl.)

680
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:55,200
(Baiye Group and Yang Jinwan now hold)

681
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,079
(a combined stake)

682
00:32:56,079 --> 00:32:57,759
(of twenty-four percent)

683
00:32:57,759 --> 00:32:59,559
(as the majority shareholders.)

684
00:32:59,759 --> 00:33:02,039
(Lysen Group holds
twenty-three percent, placing second.)

685
00:33:02,359 --> 00:33:03,359
(Yinyu Technology is at)

686
00:33:03,359 --> 00:33:05,279
(twenty-one percent, and remain in third.)

687
00:33:05,519 --> 00:33:08,200
(This battle for equity
has become more unpredictable)

688
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:09,260
(with Baiye's intervention.)

689
00:33:09,279 --> 00:33:10,400
(Who will emerge victorious?)

690
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:11,599
(We'll have to wait and see.)

691
00:33:11,599 --> 00:33:12,599
Beauty Pearl Society

692
00:33:12,599 --> 00:33:13,839
is actually quite amusing.

693
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:16,580
Did you bring me here

694
00:33:17,279 --> 00:33:19,240
just to force me to watch

695
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:21,480
the news about how I'm trailing behind?

696
00:33:32,519 --> 00:33:33,319
Forgive me.

697
00:33:34,559 --> 00:33:35,799
Too much liquor lately.

698
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,000
It's rough.

699
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:38,519
I'm quitting.

700
00:33:39,039 --> 00:33:40,079
If there's nothing else,

701
00:33:40,079 --> 00:33:41,000
I'm leaving.

702
00:33:41,279 --> 00:33:42,079
Mr. Pengyu.

703
00:33:44,799 --> 00:33:45,839
You'll want to stay

704
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:48,200
and try this.

705
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:52,860
(Xian Donghai)

706
00:33:57,660 --> 00:34:00,540
(Xian Donghai)

707
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:05,680
Wait.

708
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:08,000
You knew my father?

709
00:34:09,760 --> 00:34:10,599
Beauty Pearl Society

710
00:34:10,599 --> 00:34:12,599
enjoys listening to everyone's stories.

711
00:34:13,519 --> 00:34:14,440
It helps us see

712
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,960
if there's potential for collaboration.

713
00:34:17,159 --> 00:34:18,800
We invited you here today

714
00:34:19,159 --> 00:34:21,400
because we'd like to hear
your story, Mr. Pengyu.

715
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:28,559
What story?

716
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:30,400
One where you admit

717
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:31,840
you're just a discarded pawn?

718
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:33,840
Or one where you keep

719
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:36,199
fighting to avenge your father?

720
00:34:39,900 --> 00:34:42,140
(Xian Donghai)

721
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:43,760
Mr. Pengyu,

722
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,239
which will it be today?

723
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,679
If your goal is to avenge your father,

724
00:34:59,239 --> 00:35:00,400
the Beauty Pearl Society

725
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:02,679
can show you the way.

726
00:35:07,679 --> 00:35:10,320
(4%)
A woman has the stake you're after.

727
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:12,159
She'll come to you.

728
00:35:19,740 --> 00:35:27,559
(Official's Mansion)

729
00:35:27,559 --> 00:35:28,360
Mr. Pengyu.

730
00:35:29,519 --> 00:35:30,639
We need to talk.

731
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:33,320
Well, well.

732
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:34,480
The little genius herself.

733
00:35:35,199 --> 00:35:36,840
I really did underestimate you.

734
00:35:37,400 --> 00:35:39,239
Who would've thought
a good guy like you

735
00:35:39,239 --> 00:35:40,599
actually had an ace up her sleeve?

736
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:43,039
Of course good people have leverage.

737
00:35:44,239 --> 00:35:45,920
It just depends on how and when

738
00:35:46,199 --> 00:35:47,079
they choose to use it.

739
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,760
So tell me,

740
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:50,559
Mr. Pengyu.

741
00:35:51,199 --> 00:35:52,519
If you actually win,

742
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,760
what's your next move?

743
00:36:04,700 --> 00:36:08,300
=Episode 21=
(Shattered)

744
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:11,260
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

745
00:36:11,260 --> 00:36:17,460
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

746
00:36:18,220 --> 00:36:21,420
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

747
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:25,940
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

748
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:33,460
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

749
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:37,380
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

750
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:41,420
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

751
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:44,940
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

752
00:36:44,940 --> 00:36:48,900
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

753
00:36:48,900 --> 00:36:53,060
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

754
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:57,260
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

755
00:36:57,260 --> 00:37:01,060
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

756
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:05,140
♪Keep walking through the light♪

757
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:09,340
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

758
00:37:09,340 --> 00:37:15,660
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

759
00:37:32,780 --> 00:37:39,420
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

760
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:43,260
♪An apology that came too late♪

761
00:37:43,260 --> 00:37:47,900
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

762
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:55,380
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

763
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:59,460
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

764
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:03,540
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

765
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:07,540
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

766
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:11,300
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

767
00:38:11,300 --> 00:38:15,500
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

768
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:19,660
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

769
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:23,380
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

770
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:27,420
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

771
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:31,460
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

772
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:37,660
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
